Welcome to Keigo

There’s 7 billion unique personalities, but we all have one thing in common. Everyone wants to be heard and understood. Keigo is the new way to easily connect with different people and understand their preferences.

Let AI assisted psychometrics work out the personality insights of your conversation partner and tune you in, by analysing their social media footprint or any text they’ve written.

You can become a communication Jedi by letting Keigo help you understand, manage and enhance different social situations.

How AI helps you to understand better

The world becomes a lot nicer when we human understand each other better. Keigo is powered by Watson, the most disruptive and advanced Artificial Intelligence, so that you can improve the way you connect with people. Go Keigo and make the world a better place.

There for you in any situation

Whether you have an important interview, a first date or a social event - imagine, what your life will be like when you connect just a little better with the people you meet.

and mutual understanding during any meeting

Your secret weapon that helps you connect better

Keigo makes social situations a little better and helps you connect easier in important situations. You’ll have advanced psychology and cutting-edge AI gadget in your pocket. Weigh your words or shoot from the hip – Keigo will tell you. Go Keigo and create unique chemistry.
